2026-05-02T02:39:07.0517634Z 12    <!--
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0518045Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0518429Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
