2026-05-02T02:39:07.0524311Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0524678Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0525019Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0525387Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0525737Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0526112Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0526470Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0526828Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0527132Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-02T02:39:07.0527301Z 32    -->
